data.description: Great single-level rancher in the The Village at Elk Ridge.  This well cared for 3 bedroom 2 bath home sits on 1.06 acres with views of surrounding mountain ranges.  Easy 35 minute commute to downtown Bozeman and 25 minutes to the Bozeman Airport.  Enjoy hiking, fishing and golfing all within minutes of the up and coming and charming town of Three Forks Montana.  The home has many upgrades including ship lap accent walls, in-ceiling speakers and wiring for home theatre, beautiful quartz counters and all stainless appliances.  The wood stove and radiant flooring throughout make this a very warm and inviting home.  A must see!
